<h1>Rules and Scoring</h1>
<p>This section explains the rules and scoring system used by F1 Tips.</p>

<h4>REGISTRATION</h4>
<p>All entry money must be paid by the start of round 3 (for Season 2018 only; 2019 onwards will be round 1)</p>

<p>All tips must be submitted via the website by the start of Qualifying at each round. The website shows Qualifying start time for each event in AEST. In the event of the website being down submit tips via email to f1tips@agoralogic.com or by WhatsApp message to 'you know who'.</p>

<h4>SCORING</h4>
<p>Each race you must select a 3 different drivers for Qualification session, 3 different drivers for Race session and 1 drivcer for 10th place during the race.</p>

<p>Qualification selections are scored based on the official qualification position of each driver during the qualification session.  Any penalties that are applied after qualificaiton session but before the race that affect the drivers starting position do not affect the qualificaiton results.  For any doubt, the qualificaiton scoring is based on qualificaiton results, not race start position.</p>

